originalText.text: Isaac was a source of candor, reason, and hope throughout our firstborn's college process. He helped us cut through the misconceptions and much of the angst of a fraught system. He quickly developed his own rapport with our son and fostered (see how I did that? :) a productive dialogue within our family, enabling us to keep every step authentic to our son's story and our family's values. Isaac was consistently accessible for everything we needed, nothing less and nothing more than we wanted. We had FUN together and are excited to work with him again as we approach our younger son's journey!

originalText.text: Isaac helped both my sons through the college application process and for both of them Isaac was a game changer. His enthusiastic yet candid manner makes teens comfortable while also motivating them to listen up and work at their highest level.  I have referred numerous families to Isaac and they all report that Isaac got their teens to engage like noone else, with outstanding results.
